  "summary": "Leo finds a mysterious note in a library book one rainy day.",
  "coverScene": "A young man sits on a wooden library floor, holding an old book with a small, folded piece of paper tucked inside.",
  "levels": {
    "B2": {
      "paragraphs": [
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo loved the quiet atmosphere of the local library.",
              "audioStart": 0.1,
              "audioEnd": 2.763
            },
            {
              "text": "He spent every afternoon there, surrounded by tall shelves of books.",
              "audioStart": 3.625,
              "audioEnd": 7.338
            },
            {
              "text": "One rainy Tuesday, he found a small, handwritten note inside a dusty novel.",
              "audioStart": 8.2,
              "audioEnd": 12.725
            },
            {
              "text": "The message was simple, asking if anyone else enjoyed the beauty of old stories.",
              "audioStart": 13.588,
              "audioEnd": 17.788
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo felt a strange spark of excitement as he read the words.",
              "audioStart": 18.65,
              "audioEnd": 21.762
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "He decided that he would write a reply to the unknown reader.",
              "audioStart": 22.625,
              "audioEnd": 25.475
            },
            {
              "text": "He placed his response within the same book before returning it to the shelf.",
              "audioStart": 26.337,
              "audioEnd": 30.238
            },
            {
              "text": "The next day, Leo returned to the library with a hopeful heart.",
              "audioStart": 31.1,
              "audioEnd": 34.487
            },
            {
              "text": "He checked the book again, wondering if the stranger had seen his note.",
              "audioStart": 35.35,
              "audioEnd": 38.913
            },
            {
              "text": "To his surprise, a new letter was waiting for him.",
              "audioStart": 39.775,
              "audioEnd": 42.438
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "They continued this secret exchange for several weeks.",
              "audioStart": 43.3,
              "audioEnd": 46.125
            },
            {
              "text": "Each note revealed a new detail about their lives and their favorite characters.",
              "audioStart": 46.987,
              "audioEnd": 50.987
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo began to imagine what the person might look like.",
              "audioStart": 51.85,
              "audioEnd": 54.625
            },
            {
              "text": "He wanted to meet them, but he feared that the magic would disappear.",
              "audioStart": 55.487,
              "audioEnd": 58.938
            },
            {
              "text": "If he spoke to them, would the mystery remain as special as it was now?",
              "audioStart": 59.8,
              "audioEnd": 63.175
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "One afternoon, Leo decided to stay late near the bookshelf.",
              "audioStart": 64.037,
              "audioEnd": 67.287
            },
            {
              "text": "He waited in the shadows, watching the entrance of the library.",
              "audioStart": 68.15,
              "audioEnd": 71.25
            },
            {
              "text": "A young woman walked toward the shelf where they kept their notes.",
              "audioStart": 72.112,
              "audioEnd": 75.062
            },
            {
              "text": "She reached for the book, and Leo realized that he had to say something.",
              "audioStart": 75.925,
              "audioEnd": 79.638
            },
            {
              "text": "His heart beat fast as he stepped out from behind the corner.",
              "audioStart": 80.5,
              "audioEnd": 83.5
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The woman looked up, her eyes wide with surprise.",
              "audioStart": 84.362,
              "audioEnd": 87.138
            },
            {
              "text": "She held the book tightly, not knowing if she should smile or run away.",
              "audioStart": 88,
              "audioEnd": 91.65
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo explained that he was the person who wrote the notes.",
              "audioStart": 92.513,
              "audioEnd": 95.275
            },
            {
              "text": "A soft, nervous laugh escaped her lips as she recognized him.",
              "audioStart": 96.138,
              "audioEnd": 99.625
            },
            {
              "text": "Finally, they began to talk, and the story of their friendship truly started.",
              "audioStart": 100.487,
              "audioEnd": 104.763
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
